{
  "stem": "13584.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the border, they slept somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Sura woke up next day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said she doesn't want to go anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father asked, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The dream told me to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, she disappeared during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he went to, to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he worked over there in Brest, Brest-Litosvk-- it was named into Russian-- as a waiter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, apparently-- how he done it, I don't know-- he sent for me and for my mother, his wife.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went, we went, obviously, illegally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We crossed the border between Poland and Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As we know now, Russia had an agreement with Germans, the Nonaggression Pact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was illegal to cross the border from Poland to Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But some, some soldiers there, apparently-- that's what my mother said-- looked away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They pretended they don't see the refugees crossing the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, we came to Brest-Litovsk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lived there, I think, a few months or a half-year, a year, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the conversations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apparently, there were conversation between mother and father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't remember these conversations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was too, too, too tiny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Too young.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the journey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, the border, the border between Poland and Russia was moved far to the west, because Russians obviously took away a huge part of Poland in 1939.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The journey, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do remember that we were crossing the border, night time, and the border, the earth, the soil of the border was plowed, you know, so that those who were standing on the border, guarding the border, would see steps if somebody crosses the border illegally.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
